    %h1.title
      About
    %p
      Built by hobbyists for hobbyists.
    
    %p
      The Pursuit of Hobbiness is a collection of guides, gear, and fun things required for hobbies.  It's maintained by Michael, an engineer who lives in the California Bay Area.  Michael has a lot of hobbies and has has bought a lot of things over the years for support them.  He thought it would be fun to put them in one place and to share his research with other people.